	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi all,
<br />
<br />are there any methods that I can drive NES into
<br />a "power-saving" or "sleep" mode so that minimal
<br />power will be consumed while it can be awakened
<br />by timers?
<br />
<br />Blanc

		

		</td>
	</tr>
