	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Okay, here's my idea for a sleep mode.
<br />
<br />1. Disable sprites and background bits in $2001.
<br />2. Disable sound bits in $4015.
<br />3. Execute the undocumented opcode KIL or HLT.
<br />4. Make damn sure your victim knows to hit the reset button.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


